      public boolean canShowBranchSuffixPanel()
      Don't show Branch Suffix Panel if any of the following is true 1) initial clone is not completed yet (helper.Context.IsSetupComplete is false) 2) product tree is not valid 3) not deployed pc
      Returns:
      true or false based on the above condition

      public void checkBranchNameAndShowErrorMessage(String branchSuffix)
      Checks to see if the passed in branchSuffix can be used to create a new branch for each helper. If the branchSuffix can not be used (e.g. - the branch already exists for a given repository), a web error message will be added.
      Parameters:
      branchSuffix -
